Package: caabgp
Type: Package
Title: Cost-Aware Adaptive-Borrowing Gaussian-Process Bayesian Optimization
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hao", "Chen", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "hche2036@uni.sydney.edu.au"),
    person("Clara", "Grazian", role = "aut")
  )
Author: Hao Chen [aut, cre], Clara Grazian [aut]
Maintainer: Hao Chen <hche2036@uni.sydney.edu.au>
Description: Empirical-Bayes Gaussian-process Bayesian optimization tools for
    personalized combination dose-finding trials. The package implements the
    cost-aware adaptive-borrowing Gaussian-process design with finite dose grids,
    operational costs, and stratum-specific recommendations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
